defaultation in the council tax support which has resulted in benefit being cut from 100% to only a few pounds. DHP has been awarded for 3 months. The couple need a very large 2 bed or face placing their daughter in a care home to widen their options to a one-bed
defaultroom. The likelihood of securing alternative accommodation in 3 months is very low.
